noting that $X$ and $Y$ lie on $\Gamma$.
As $\ol{XF} \parallel \ol{AB}$ we can let $M$
denote the midpoint of minor arcs $\widehat{XF}$ and $\widehat{AB}$
(which coincide). Define $N$ similarly.

