$\arc{AX}$, $\arc{XY}$, $\arc{YZ}$, $\arc{ZB}$, respectively,
so that $\alpha + \beta + \gamma + \delta = 90\dg$.

\begin{center}
\begin{asy}
pair A = dir(180);
