Let $O$ be the center of $\omega$,
and let $M = \ol{PQ} \cap \ol{AB}$ and $N = \ol{PQ} \cap \ol{AC}$
be the midpoints of $\ol{AB}$ and $\ol{AC}$ respectively.
Refer to the diagram below.

